preference.name: Baseline_consider_all_statuses
preference.preference_description: Activates considering all release statuses attached to Item Revisions, while creating baselines for released Item Revisions. Valid Values: * false: Only the latest release status on Item Revisions is considered. * true: All release statuses present on Item Revisions are considered.
